{"tid":1096757,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慎入】\u001c內地藝術家清明挖父遺骨自照！ 終極版「懷念爺爺」","createTime":"2019-04-08T02:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T04:41:21.000Z","uid":141060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6edc582b0a362b0054089398c40b947977e6e1c","tid":1096757,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190407/_2019040719035438123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190407%2F_2019040719035438123.jpg&h=6ac5208f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n司原逐冀一系列與父骨的合照惹來極大爭議。微博<br />\n清明節祭祖是傳統活動，內地一名藝術家卻以現代行為藝術重新演繹，惹來極大爭議。藝術家司原逐冀上周在清明節竟將父親的遺骨挖出，並全裸與骨骸合照。有網民抨擊是「污辱藝術」，借先人炒作；也有人表示看了很心酸。目前司原逐冀的微博及微信已被封鎖，相關影像亦被移除。<br />\n<br />\n內地新銳藝術家司原逐冀昨日在微博上分享了一系列圖像，內容是家人為28歲就因病早逝的父親進行移墓。他表示，自己年幼時父親就亡故，除了遺照外對他沒有印象。因為這日剛好在撿骨，所以想跟父親一起合照。<br />\n<br />\n司原逐冀續稱，因為怕家人對他的行為不諒解，所以直接和在旁協助的撿骨師溝通，並請求妻子擔任「父子合照」的攝影師。但當將他上傳到網路後，卻引發了軒然大波。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190407/_2019040719211355229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190407%2F_2019040719211355229.jpg&h=7f627212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190407/_2019040719201044846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190407%2F_2019040719201044846.jpg&h=9c60ad74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n司原逐冀一系列與父骨的合照惹來極大爭議。微博<br />\n網民怒批他是為求知名度，「商業性行為藝術，販賣死了30年的爹」、「走投無路賺眼球」、「尊重個人意願對吧？他尊重他爹沒有？他爹同意他這樣做了嗎？」也有網友表示，能夠感受他的心情，稱「這是一種獨特的紀念，獨特的生死體驗」、「看了還挺心酸的」、「看哭了，視覺和精神的衝擊」、「尊重每個人的想法」。<br />\n<br />\n司原逐冀在中國藝術圈一直備受爭議，之前展出有關裸露、色情、暴力的作品，也遭人批評「打著藝術的幌子，散播色情暴力」、「玷汙新銳，拿女性的隱私做行為藝術」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190407/_2019040719201038810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190407%2F_2019040719201038810.jpg&h=6e1a9af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190407/_2019040719035670227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190407%2F_2019040719035670227.jpg&h=dc21fa07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190407/_2019040719035644213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190407%2F_2019040719035644213.jpg&h=a6a1694a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190407/_2019040719035770199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190407%2F_2019040719035770199.jpg&h=7d5f146e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3de2f7f5ff4d30ed69c825751077240d8f88b750","tid":1096757,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625ae30f26d4bc9396459d8fefa0397f2d46d95b","tid":1096757,"uid":143598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b029de33adfc19868678fb55cc3981b53b79a2","tid":1096757,"uid":143598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/010042_2fc9f33496e88035d6ba180ea5834eb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F010042_2fc9f33496e88035d6ba180ea5834eb3.jpg&h=c2c2e8d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8b8e94e7cbdd354a61fad2613c99c67404a5d7e","tid":1096757,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dis